Damian Lillard: 'Disappointing' to hear Russell Westbrook's All-Star remarks<br />
<br />
&quot;I respect Russ a lot so it was kind of disappointing to see him say that, because he's played against me, he's played against our team, he knows what I've accomplished. Not just this year, but over my career. So it was a little bit disappointing, but I know that I earned my spot this year. And that's pretty much what it is. <span style="font-size: x-large;">I earned my spot</span>.&quot;
